{"tid":749332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾蔭權上訴定罪失敗　獲減刑至12個月須即時繼續服刑","createTime":"2018-07-20T02:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T18:02:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2042f2c6de260de81140607fc86e16888b0f0381","tid":749332,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/37369287_10156898544037448_2643651897965150208_n.png?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=9be1a10900805b0f4125e0699d63d45b&amp;oe=5BD5DEE5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F37369287_10156898544037448_2643651897965150208_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D9be1a10900805b0f4125e0699d63d45b%26oe%3D5BD5DEE5&h=c57d725e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"818a086506d94e6fba20cb6b11d9a19e883bffa8","tid":749332,"uid":33456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:02:06.000Z","msg":"幾時到689條冚家剷呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e37b3f74483e21abf14828554000f491e2e3c7","tid":749332,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:03:24.000Z","msg":"上訴庭三位法官的判決理由：<br />\n<br />\n●從陪審團的裁決看到，他們顯然不接納曾蔭權聲稱大意沒有申報的辯解<br />\n●曾蔭權至今仍沒有交代為何會做出案中行為，事件仍留有問號，「很可惜這個問號或者永遠得不到答案」。<br />\n●曾蔭權的失當行為嚴重<br />\n●曾蔭權身為特首，其行為會危害市民對政府運作的信心，亦影響香港政府對外的聲譽<br />\n●曾蔭權的罪行持續了一段時間，即時監禁是合適的判刑。<br />\n●原審量刑起點太高，合適的起點應是18個月<br />\n●基於曾的良好品格及過往對香港的貢獻，減刑6個月，總刑期為12個月。"},{"pid":"3266f682dff2372c451ef6f74592cbeb23539437","tid":749332,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:03:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f2e4524a73a62f54a1885ddfc4a56b6b2da488a","tid":749332,"uid":75394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:22:16.000Z","msg":"1年姐<img src=\"/assets/f